PSIHELP: Psionic help shortcut

Syntax: psihelp
        psihelp <topic>

DESCRIPTION:
  Opens psionic help. With no argument, shows the full psionics overview.
  With a topic, shows help for that psionic command or power.

  Examples:
    psihelp
    psihelp psi
    psihelp telepathy
    psihelp psionics

NOTES:
  This is a shortcut for help psionics and related psionic topics.
  You must have psionic access through your race or OCC to use psi powers.

SEE ALSO: psionics, psi, telepathy, isp, meditate
